From ca71489aa82cfc66c67ecd616696e826dc6e7e7a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Benjamin Fuchs <benjamin.fuchs@adorsys.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 10:35:41 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 4/5] fix(br): extend coverage quality calibration (Block E)

- Add extended quality insufficiency reasons:
  - non_business_surface_spike: high ratio of non-business surface drops
  - schema_only_spike: high ratio of schema-only drops
  - governance_meta_rule_spike: high ratio of governance meta rejections
  - insufficient_executable_business_rules: very low executable business rule ratio
- Add new metrics:
  - post_drop_valid_ratio: fraction of discovery-passed candidates that are valid
  - executable_business_rule_ratio: fraction of raw candidates that are executable business rules
- Add fields to CodeExtractionCoverage dataclass
---
